<title>大模型们拿着锤子找钉钉</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E4%BB%AC%E6%8B%BF%E7%9D%80%E9%94%A4%E5%AD%90%E6%89%BE%E9%92%89%E9%92%89</link>
<content:encoded>&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_thumb_wrp&quot; id=&quot;media&quot;&gt;

